{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "87816140-e43c-412e-9bbe-e90bac2aab6a",
    "name": "Science1-06-Geology",
    "sceneId": "4c80661d-0537-46d4-b6d6-422313186fac",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "d9d74b2e-24b7-4221-84c6-efa6f9befaae",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "201f984c-1769-43ce-8c8f-2945067db6ab",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "5a822184-922d-42a9-a33c-1f6f03c24e81",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Today's lecture is on Geology - the study of the world, rocks, and minerals. Now, I'm sure that some of you budding geologists have rock collections at home. We'll be talking about how rocks are made and where to find them.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "871797de-0beb-4dad-84c0-6c93bab3867c",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "The island of Sardonia is an interesting study in Geology. Years ago, this entire region was disrupted by volcanoes. ",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "4202c2a4-fb94-407d-b4b5-d5156e862a91",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Thus, much of the rock forming the hills of this island is igneous in nature. This explains the deposits of Sulphur that can be found here.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "dafa21a9-d562-49c2-a43c-ad005853d65c",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "On the other hand, rock formed by layers of silt and dirt over the ages was pushed up from the sea floor. Most of Sardonia is composed of sedimentary rock. ",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "1bd39c07-65a9-406e-a8b9-2bbf84ba7f75",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "This means that there are veins of Phosphorus running through this island in the form of phosphate.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "5bfa298a-3fcc-468c-9f20-2af9e6e0e660",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Phosphorus is a fascinating mineral. It glows in the dark, makes a pungent, probably poisonous gas, and can be used in explosives. We'll be investigating the latter property in several lessons.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "d7b20d64-4a43-40be-9b50-24df78076466",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are there any questions about what we've covered so far?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "4df64fa5-dd5a-461e-9f1d-5df59b879ec2",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "97b75fd0-97ee-4cc7-ba9c-eef1c5e54bca",
                            "text": "Gush About Geology",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "df33293a-c486-47a1-8cb5-b0e730ab0705",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "30",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "c2c09f13-0143-4ed4-88f0-6fecef62592a",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "47bd43c9-9c8b-47f2-96be-362ec1f9535f",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "Wow, I didn't know that geology was so interesting... Or that Sardonia had both igneous and sedimentary rocks. This takes my knowledge to whole new levels.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "4c9d50a0-9fa4-4d1a-8833-5d072915f249",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Science frees the mind from the blinders of superstition and allows people to see just how astonishing even the rocks themselves can be.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "71f35929-2e48-458f-a5df-28e7ff8d8382",
                            "text": "Ask About Sardonia's Geology",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "8cbe1110-51ce-4b86-80a9-5ac6d0db46af",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "30",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "5ffb9fac-4efb-4e5f-9aee-93bd8bd04a85",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "88108ab7-0a45-4572-95fc-16cd312deae8",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "What do you mean when you say that Sardonia is mostly sedimentary rock?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "e181ab89-890b-4ba9-b256-bb8c4136168c",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Much of the terrain of Sardonia is a combination of limestone studded with phosphate nodules, which explains why there are huge Sea Caves under much of the island. Sedimentary rock erodes easily.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7855a24e-1d78-4f8f-975e-46c49878fea0",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "However, there is an underlying strata of volcanic rock forming the core of the island. There are even some indications that there are active chambers of magma underneath areas of Sardonia.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "e065d44a-a17c-443d-ac74-c8cefe8938af",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "By Geologist standards, one cannot just take this island for granite!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "b00690fc-44ff-499d-bfe8-f28fe3932758",
                            "text": "Make a Geology Joke",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "142f7ae7-464e-4241-b0ca-73f3a443c476",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "30",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "ee0f0d1f-c8dd-47e7-bb21-2cf44cc5b019",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "095e6ee7-e7a2-43ec-8069-e1195867bf3d",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "Does this mean that Geologists are down to 'earth' people and very Sedimental?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d6dfceff-8443-49f6-8ea1-f80a5c2b6111",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Most geologists are genuinely gneiss people.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                    "Unique": true
                },
                {
